Name: gridmap
Version: 0.13.0
Summary: Easily map Python functions onto a cluster using a DRMAA-compatible grid engine like Sun Grid Engine (SGE).
Home-page: http://github.com/EducationalTestingService/gridmap
Author: Daniel Blanchard
